reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2020
reviews.reviewText: Spectacular knives! I bought these for my daughter and son in law because their kitchen knives are deplorable! I’ve been staying with them to help with their small children and so far I’m the only one who has used these knives, but I absolutely love them! I definitely plan to get a set for myself, my mom, and my other daughter and son in law!I shopped through knife sets for several hours before settling on these. One of the biggest selling points for me was that they didn’t come with steak knives or in a tacky block! My daughter has very young children whom are very active and curious. She keeps her sharp implements in a childproof drawer, not on the counter, so a countertop knife block would not work. As for the lack of steak knives, I appreciated that this set did not include them. I was looking for quality cooking knives, not service knives. So many of the other sets I considered came with 6 steak knives (in order to market a 15-piece set, I suspect), which aren’t necessary in my daughter’s home, and detract from the true value of the overall sets.I love that these knives are simply cooking knives without the fluff. The handles are comfortable to grip, ergonomic and lightweight. They are razor sharp too! They came in a lovely gift box that is worth keeping! And they’re just beautiful and so wonderful to work with!Love the lifetime warranty and the very attentive follow up customer service after purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are the best knives I’ve bought! Very sharp and makes cutting an ease! Be careful and I would advise protective gloves for beginners. I don’t like things on my counter so I love the sleek storage box. Also, if you plan to keep in the box DO NOT throw away the plastic protectors on the pointy end of the knives.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Knives are very sharp and well made. I had a small problem and the company took care of it immediately. I couldn't ask for better service. They were caring and prompt. I am very satisfied .

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very frustrating, how I am going to sharpen them?
reviews.reviewText: They are sharp OK, I like the covers on the blades, but handles and slippery. I don't know how to sharpen them ease... Not sure...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I have used dull knives for at least 28 years. Growing up I was sawing potatos and anything that needed cutting. I finally decided at the ripe age of 39 I was going to buy some knives. I didnt want to spend 3oo dollars though! I took a risk and order these knives AND THEY HAVE CHANGED MY LIFE! Never knew that I could literally just slice through a potato before! THese knives are amazing and at an amazing price. they are also beautiful. The handles are really smooth so it is difficult to get a good grip if your hands are greasy in any way (from cooking or too much lotion). They also have a smooth edge which means you can get most of them sharpened (except for the small serrated knife). Totally worth it and want to gift them for my mom one of these days. She is still sawing her vegetables:(

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I have had these knives for about 3 years now. They are holding up great and they are one of my favorite knives in my drawer. After many uses and washes the only thing bad I would say is that the handle design/paint is starting to chip off a little. However, the actual blade quality has not changed since day one. Very happy with this set and I wished they also made scissors for the kitchen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 15, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great knives at a great value!
reviews.reviewText: I love the way these knives look. They're beautiful as well as functional. They come very sharp and fit my hand perfectly. The only downside is they don't hold the edge very long. After sharpening they keep the edge for a little while, usually long enough for me to finish what I'm cutting that day but the next time I need to use them I have to resharpen them. Other than that, these are excellent knives, well balanced and ergonomic. I'm very happy with my purchase and would definitely recommend them to anyone looking for professional qualityat an affordable price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got these for my grandfather but I want to steal them! These are amazing knives, super super sharp, easy to clean. I highly recommend leaving them in the box they came in if you don't have a specific place to store them. I wouldn't do drawer storage, especially if you have kids. The blade covers are great but you definitely want to take all safety precautions with these!Happy slicing and dicing!

Ero in cerca di un set di coltelli che avessero sia un'ottima qualità, sia un bell'aspetto. Il prodotto è andato incontro ad entrambe le mie esigenze. Sono leggeri e facilmente maneggevoli, quando vengono portati a tavola fanno anche la loro ottima figura.

Calidad vs precio: no me convenció, uso muchos en mi cocina de casa, y la verdad los pedí, porque me parecía una buena opción, sin embargo unas ves usados, diría que la calidad es regular, se destiñe el mango al poco tiempo de uso, el metal no es muy resistente y la hoja se destiñe también, para mí un fiasco total

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on September 1, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Its a beautiful set and very good quality

reviews.reviewTitle: No se ajusta a la realidad
reviews.reviewText: El artículo vino con un defecto en la capa negra, no estaba totalmente lacada. Además, la propia caja de los cuchillos es la caja de embalaje, con lo que todas las puntas llegaron chafadas.

Avevo bisogno di un set di coltelli nella mia cucina e questi si abbinano perfettamente ad essa, oltre ad essere eleganti sono affilatissimi e leggeri. Ideali per chi cerca qualità e robustezza nello stesso tempo. La confezione si presenta con stile, e ogni coltello ha la propria fascia di protezione per la lama da utilizzare se si vuole posizionare il coltello in qualche cassetto per preservarla. Spedizione Amazon puntuale come sempre.
